title: Cosmic Journeys
description:
[img]http://bayimg.com/kapBBAAFi[/img]

Cosmic Journey is a science show on SpaceRip TV that explores the galactic makeup of the universe. The show sets out to answer some of the most basic of human questions in a vast and relatively unexplored area of knowledge the Final frontier. The series starts with trying to answer where the universe came from and tries, by the finale, to answer where it will end. From destructive asteroids to what theoretically might be on the other side of a black hole, Cosmic Journey is just that, a journey into the universe in its entirety and our human place within it.
